snippet.title: Cats are the kings of animal comedy - Funny cat compilation
snippet.description:
Cats are simply the kings of animal comedy! They make us laugh and happy! Just look how all these cats & kittens play, fail, get along with dogs, get their heads stuck in boxes, react to mirrors, make funny sounds, get angry... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com
